Package entrants.utils.graph.interfaces

Interface WeightedEdgeInterface<N extends NodeInterface>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EdgeInterface<N>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Edge
    public interface WeightedEdgeInterface<N extends NodeInterface>
extends EdgeInterface<N>
    This interface describes the features that a class that represents weighted edges linking NodeInterface objects should offer The Edges are not oriented An edge can have multiple weights, differentiated by string keys.
